text: Creature Commandos is an upcoming animated TV series based on the DC Comics team of the same name. It is the first project of the DC Universe (DCU). The series premiered on December 5, 2024 and end on January 16, 2025, after 8 episodes. == References == == Other websites == * Category:HBO Max original programming Category:American animated television series Category:Superhero television shows
